#include<cstdio>
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
	int T;
	unsigned int N;
	unsigned int C;
	unsigned int req;
	unsigned int r;
	int i;
	
	scanf("%d",&T);
	
	while(T--)
	{
		scanf("%u",&N);
		scanf("%u",&C);
		
		req =0;
		
		for(i=0;i<N;++i) 
		{
			scanf("%u",&r);
			req+=r;
		}
		
		if(req<=C) printf("Yes\n");
		else	    printf("No\n");
	}
}
